[31m-VoiceBridge is a real-time speech-to-text application designed to bridge communication gaps for people with hearing impairments.[m
[31m-It combines deep learning, distributed systems, and big data technologies to deliver accurate, scalable, and accessible transcription services.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m**VoiceBridge enables hearing-impaired users to follow real-time conversations in meetings, classrooms, or social environments with sub-second transcription latency.** Built with modern microservices architecture, it combines AI/ML models, WebSocket streaming, and accessibility-first design to deliver accurate, scalable speech-to-text services.[m
